1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Did you know your blood type could hold secrets about your health?

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:09,600
The Rh factor determines if your blood is Rh positive or negative.

3
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:13,600
It’s all about a tiny protein on red blood cells.

4
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:17,600
But here's the twist: not everyone knows their Rh status.

5
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:20,400
This can lead to serious health risks.

6
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:25,600
In pregnancy, for example, an Rh-negative mother and Rh-positive baby can cause complications.

7
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:26,800
Awareness is crucial.

8
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:31,200
Understanding your Rh factor isn't just trivia; it can save lives.

9
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:33,200
Curious about your blood type?

10
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:35,200
Get tested and stay informed.

11
00:00:35,200 --> 00:00:37,200
Follow for more science insights!
